@node "Search_Translators" "I'm looking for translators"
 Looking for translators
 =======================

I'm looking for translators for my AmigaTNC.guide. If you want to translate
AmigaTNC to your native language, please contact me. If your language isn't
already translated you will get a reply that you can start to translate.
Please don't start translating before my reply to avoid double work of
different translators.
@endnode

@node "Contact_Address" "Contact address"
Contact address


For bug reports, suggestions please contact me. Bug reports should be detailed
because I only can find a bug if I know where I have to search for. You should
me inform about your computer configuration, used packet radio programme and
the circumstances of the crash. If you have a suggestion what I can make
better, you can also contact me, but I don't know if I have enough time to
follow your suggestions.

Post address :

  Alexander Feigl
  Burachstrasse 51

  D-88250 Weingarten

  Germany

EMail:

  Alexander.Feigl@gmx.de

@endnode

@node "Known_Bugs" "Known bugs / problems"
Known Bugs


